---
---

<section id="problem" class="relative py-28 md:py-40">
  <!-- Scattered constellation dots -->
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
    <div class="animate-twinkle absolute top-[15%] right-[8%] h-0.5 w-0.5 rounded-full bg-(--color-star-dim)" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;"></div>
    <div class="animate-twinkle absolute top-[60%] right-[15%] h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-(--color-star)" style="animation-delay: 2.1s;"></div>
    <div class="animate-twinkle absolute top-[35%] left-[3%] h-0.5 w-0.5 rounded-full bg-(--color-star-dim)" style="animation-delay: 1.3s;"></div>
    <div class="animate-twinkle absolute bottom-[20%] right-[5%] h-0.5 w-0.5 rounded-full bg-(--color-star)" style="animation-delay: 0.7s;"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid items-start gap-16 lg:grid-cols-12">

      <!-- Left column: large pull quote -->
      <div class="reveal lg:col-span-5">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[13px] tracking-widest text-(--color-text-tertiary) uppercase mb-8 block">
          <span class="inline-block h-px w-8 bg-(--color-warm)"></span>
          The problem
        </span>
        <p class="font-display text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] leading-[0.95] tracking-tight text-(--color-text)">
          Your team ships faster. You <em class="text-(--color-warm)">can't keep up.</em>
        </p>
        <!-- Decorative element -->
        <div class="mt-12 h-px w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-(--color-warm) to-transparent"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right column: body text, offset down -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-6 lg:col-start-7 lg:pt-16">
        <div class="space-y-8 text-[17px] leading-[1.7] text-(--color-text-secondary)">
          <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
            AI-assisted development means your team ships faster than ever. Features
            that used to take a sprint land in a day. But the PM, the person
            responsible for directing all that building, is still manually
            synthesizing dozens of conversations and relying on memory.
          </p>

          <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
            The bottleneck moved from
            <span class="font-medium text-(--color-text)">how fast you build</span> to
            <span class="font-medium text-(--color-text)">how fast you figure out what to build</span>.
            Critical context is scattered across dozens of conversations
            with different people about overlapping problems. You miss the pattern
            because the insights are spread everywhere.
          </p>

          <p class="reveal reveal-delay-3">
            North Star turns every conversation into structured context that
            compounds over time. Context that feeds your roadmap, shapes your epics,
            grounds your feature specs, and works directly with your AI assistants.
            Patterns emerge across conversations that no single meeting reveals.
            So when you're deciding what to build next, you have the
            <span class="text-(--color-accent)">signal</span> and the speed.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
